{"tid":1288654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥 對唔住 我無辦法還你一個清白 我覺得好內疚","createTime":"2019-07-05T17:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T03:43:30.000Z","uid":219681,"like":32,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8d0975022a1c722e4b344d4648b2c76ac8cd61dc","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">達哥，對唔住</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我無辦法還你清白，我一路睇住大家誤會你，但係仍然為大局而放低左你<br />\n<br />\n由第一次響YouTube 睇你既片，到慢慢變成每日都睇Twitch直播，我自問唔係最老既一批兄弟。但你響我心目中，一路都係好重要既人生導師<br />\n你聰明，心思細密，學富五車，聽你既直播，總係覺得有學唔完既野<br />\n生活再難，我都能夠從你身上得到正能量<br />\n<br />\n你一路教我地，做人做事要多聽多想多了解，唔應該被眼前光境蒙蔽，人生苦短，要用生命行善<br />\n我，由一個守紀律既淺藍，慢慢變到今日既淺黃，走上遊行，文宣之路，內心一堆堆激動，令我對呢個家越黎越不捨<br />\n<br />\n我曾經好想好想離開香港，但係因為你響度，令我都好希望同你一齊，好好守護呢個地方<br />\n<br />\n我知道，將你既善意宏揚，做一個稱職既「文科仔」，就係我最能為你做既事<br />\n我一路都好堅持，至今亦然<br />\n我希望響革命路上，大家一路走落去，不落單，我希望大家珍惜生命，唔希望有半秒覺得無助<br />\n<br />\n每日夜晚，我都沉思，網絡世界，到底係點樣演繹呢一個「六月」<br />\n然後我拎起鍵盤，打起一堆堆掃盲文，只希望大家一直保持清醒<br />\n但，作為你既忠粉，一隻「小學雞」，我卻未能為你發聲，未能為你討一個公道<br />\n<br />\n希望你原晾我，大局當前，你既屈辱，比起香港既將來，實在微不足道<br />\n時間會証明一切，總有一日會還你清白，我一路相信‥<br />\n<br />\n我明白，你係一個負責任既人，就算好多大是大非面前，你都會為大家留退路<br />\n我明白，你既頭盔，從來都係為大家而戴<br />\n你並唔懦弱，只係因為你實在有太多負擔，太多責任，太多束縛<br />\n你想保護既，唔單單係一班兄弟，更係呢一個家<br />\n<br />\n今日既你，已經唔能夠再做「陳近南」<br />\n今日既你，每一句，每一步，都早已成為敵我既焦點<br />\n縱然你從來沒有攻擊你既敵人，但一堆人卻一直希望從你既沉默同失勢中「得益」<br />\n<br />\n見到你失勢，我曾經有半刻高興，因為我好想你可以擺脫束縛，可以做自己想做既事，玩自己想玩既遊戲<br />\n我亦都好想你可以只做自己，唔需要照顧太多道德，唔需要照顧太多觀眾既感受<br />\n係我地成就左你，但我地亦都毀左你既自由<br />\n<br />\n睇住一堆堆網紅，忽然勇武，忽視民主，我不恥，但我亦唔可以打擊<br />\n因為不割席，不決裂，不指責，我堅持，只要係對件事好，我就會做<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，大家努力多日，成果未現，第一日被踢落山既反而係你<br />\n你既忍耐，卻不幸令大家將對你既期望，慢慢轉為失望，甚至轉為怒氣，然後再將所有不快都推到你身<br />\n<br />\n無論講咩都好，你都受盡攻擊<br />\n今日，連你不忍同路人「送頭」，都仍然被批評<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻既你，壓力之大，絕非當年Backup事件可比<br />\n我唔知道可以點幫你，每日收工，我都響地鐵站A出口徘徊，希望能夠見到你<br />\n同你講一聲鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n我明白你既苦處，你既傲骨。你選擇沉默，你選擇唔澄清，唔反駁，我亦選擇相信你<br />\n由活動開始至今，眼見你每每被拖出黎批評，我每每只能按壓心中既怒火<br />\n要打擊你既人，少不了私怨的一群，少不了五毛的一群<br />\n但不得不承認，亦有不少兄弟，一路都因為沒有收到你既表態而失望<br />\n<br />\nKen Louis 兄弟亦係其中一位<br />\n我其實一路都好欣賞佢，佢真係好有耐心去經營剪輯你既片<br />\n今日佢誤會左你，佢唔能夠原晾你，其實我比你更加傷心<br />\n但我唔支持大家去攻擊佢，因為佢既率性，都係因為一顆「赤子之心」<br />\n佢既失望，同眾多兄弟一樣，都係源自對你既「過多期望」<br />\n<br />\n我無辦法幫你講太多，因為我只有一把口，沒法子推倒一波怒濤<br />\n我只希望你會明白，你既沉默，並不孤單。你既身旁仍然有我，同一班兄弟，我地仍然響同一個時空，「真兄弟會明白」，仍然係我地之間既默契<br />\n<br />\n我知道你一直都在，你並唔係大家眼中既「漠不關心」<br />\n呢一陣子，你從忽然男神，再回歸一個毒男既內心，呢份落差，實在唔係筆墨可以形容<br />\n但所有野都唔重要，最重要係你要快樂阿<br />\n<br />\n有人話你棋差一著，但我知道，你既選擇只是想保護要保護既人<br />\n討厭「黑警」既你，根本唔可能「歸順」<br />\n今日既你，縱使沒有站在「撐警」大會既舞台，但卻落得比何妖更差的污名<br />\n係兄弟不好，我求你原晾我<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無論你認識我與否，請聽我一言：回來吧</span></strong><br />\n兄弟們都很想你"},{"pid":"feb4794ba917261af22644418f80e9bcb2707188","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fec4de1c942d9a228c070c6fbdd4e89de90b040","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5931d8e512d325e3445d77b2fc0320762e157641","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e382df44643d30c123ecce57e07622faa38ff","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03315d7fc0b980dd8b551fb21b218f0e8c7d1a21","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d2db644c64c0ace3a960d62d3c2a1439a2f7af","tid":1288654,"uid":87552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b555501d7e7b627f985b076c4a780155921d8f","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"講真，你睇完，覺得唔岩聽，負評，唔緊要<br />\n但希望你地自己保持清醒既思維，唔好「人云亦云」<br />\n獨立思想先係爭取自由意志既重中之重"},{"pid":"54dfbfa52ba2adf87ae9c2d1088b82fb97ab72e7","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52d2db644c64c0ace3a960d62d3c2a1439a2f7af","tid":1288654,"uid":87552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f45fbb052d7959093e97f721f7e3fed64258097","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feceefb269799504102ca3431a414fcc5e1bb9de","tid":1288654,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"掛念達子"},{"pid":"6b4a9af2212c5de8af96ee1eb57ba9407c3b4f94","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"達哥，以上係我真心想同你講既野<br />\n支持你阿"},{"pid":"e79f8c8be616827f40b0219f872f46f4e6f8a5b4","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b91eb859a7497ff04ac395e96a0f365b94c4e39","tid":1288654,"uid":92459,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"獨立思想<br />\n係反送中初頭仲好多人撐佢既時候我已經屌緊佢"},{"pid":"8fc334633c260d3044d4701e60afb7d16ceb93b2","tid":1288654,"uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"達哥：無論你鍾意我與否，請聽我一言：不要輕生。<br />\n達哥係完美世界M等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9V9krtq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V9krtq.gif&h=2a465aae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"517d4858ad8de1f49f2f356bff798fe1bfdfe10e","tid":1288654,"uid":219276,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢啲好聽叫痴情<br />\n唔好聽叫On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講到佢咁偉大啦<br />\n喺利益同良心之間<br />\n佢已經做咗佢嘅選擇"},{"pid":"1aa55acd274a13b7d84c8444fea0998e2fd10c8f","tid":1288654,"uid":29510,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n呢個世界已經變到只用政治去評定功過<br />\n連登仔呢班兄弟只有要求，沒有體諒<br />\n<br />\n但又打住兄弟旗號，話好失望<br />\n同時打住兄弟旗號，不斷追擊，一沉百踩<br />\n<br />\n所有野再加句&lsquo;大是大非前xxxx&rsquo;，就變到好合理<br />\n<br />\n大家對佢有期望，好正常<br />\n但如果當佢兄弟，道不同，咪不相為謀，何必一路消費佢<br />\n<br />\n達哥個立場一早表達左，佢只係想俾個無政治干擾既兩個鐘俾人輕鬆下"},{"pid":"96e361d6d5a2e8a1e7de66ce981e09facf6f60f6","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b91eb859a7497ff04ac395e96a0f365b94c4e39","tid":1288654,"uid":92459,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"獨立思想<br />\n係反送中初頭仲好多人撐佢既時候我已經屌緊佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:35:04.000Z","msg":"兄弟<br />\n我想同你解釋一下點解公眾人物唔可以表態<br />\n事實証明，好多人會利用政治立場去打擊對方<br />\n呢樣野根本唔係邊一面出得多錢既問題<br />\n<br />\n達哥既一堆代言，代表左一間間公司既生意同立場<br />\n佢既一句說話，可以令好多人轉為攻擊曾經搵佢代言既公司<br />\n呢個係責任問題<br />\n<br />\n事實上好多藝人都唔敢公開表態<br />\n只係大家從一開始就俾一班有心人將個矛頭指左落達哥度<br />\n慢慢變成達哥唔表態就係「奶共」<br />\n今日仲有人話佢「支持送中」<br />\n<br />\n如果你有時間，不妨去起下底，攻擊達哥既呢一班友當中有幾多五毛"},{"pid":"45e42cbd893098d3e41dd1b61361916a12964e41","tid":1288654,"uid":183358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"食屎啦死達狗， 咪又係睇咗人哋嗰個post先出聲 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287052\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287052</a>"},{"pid":"3b319a82a595e220d0bd0d37b1f49b808e7f519f","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517d4858ad8de1f49f2f356bff798fe1bfdfe10e","tid":1288654,"uid":219276,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢啲好聽叫痴情<br />\n唔好聽叫On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講到佢咁偉大啦<br />\n喺利益同良心之間<br />\n佢已經做咗佢嘅選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:37:44.000Z","msg":"我係好鍾意佢，但我都曾經懷疑過自己係咪唔認識佢呢<br />\n如果你有留意表左態既藝人，你會明白一個公眾人物表態，已經唔單單係個人立場，而係團隊立場，已經唔係個人代價，係「累街坊」既問題<br />\n如果有一日你去到果個位置，或者你都會明白"},{"pid":"18c9515c06fd6d44430aee0c2174975680090bb0","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc334633c260d3044d4701e60afb7d16ceb93b2","tid":1288654,"uid":85180,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"達哥：無論你鍾意我與否，請聽我一言：不要輕生。<br />\n達哥係完美世界M等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9V9krtq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V9krtq.gif&h=2a465aae&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:44:08.000Z","msg":"其實好多直播主，都代言唔少國產遊戲<br />\n國產並唔係原罪，唔需要黎黎去去都用呢樣野攻擊達哥<br />\n<br />\n你可以睇下Steam既遊戲排名，其中有一隻國產Game<br />\n隱形守護者，係好多台灣直播主都玩緊<br />\n呢隻Game 一樣冇繁體，點解冇人批評 ?<br />\n<br />\n佢地攻擊達哥，只係想拉低佢黎提高自己既知名度<br />\n點解大家唔可以清醒少少，將焦點放番響遊戲內容"},{"pid":"793f39ac0581baa5cb48439c414be4c587c60e6f","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e42cbd893098d3e41dd1b61361916a12964e41","tid":1288654,"uid":183358,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"食屎啦死達狗， 咪又係睇咗人哋嗰個post先出聲 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287052\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287052</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"睇到你個名，都唔知點答你好"},{"pid":"44156a85534dffdbb01417d2112408b569ce9ba6","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193a3e1e38b118f001372215db0d90e4050b8fed","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597d307d35322f0c0e69fdb2a61637ad84502afe","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f7883e72ff86afcbac36676aa10bf092493e42","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50c18c3ba6bb7253c27f63d648ca1521f841d0a","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"下面係兩個好好例子 唔該自己思考一下<br />\n<br />\n玩夠啦，番去睇達哥開台啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1288686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1288686</a><br />\n<br />\n各位，達哥已經改邪歸正，請大家原諒佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1288663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1288663</a>"},{"pid":"1ade93c19fd66d0f851bb626cf272353fa7c1b9e","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cc4576ed928086524e013e3c0966c1b2a12236","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b419483c176934a155bdaca67b1076b0f4991d98","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5d58afc5fe74462538aac48693a0f73cb97347","tid":1288654,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"我認為佢係俾人故意狙擊<br />\n點解咁多KOL唔恰，就係恰佢？<br />\n因為佢平時啲冤屈好多都自己吞咗佢唔出聲算<br />\n轉game世界大戰如是<br />\nbackup佢事件如是<br />\n今次唔出聲，終於搞到收唔到科<br />\n<br />\n本人真誠相信，佢嘅立場不變"},{"pid":"563a3ebec99e3a350f502b37d0d990f5b60b987e","tid":1288654,"uid":262647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:07:22.000Z","msg":"預左比人屌<br />\n唔係為達哥平反 只係純粹個人表達<br />\n我覺得公眾人物都有佢既因素<br />\n佢公開帶頭係呀 呢個政權係點點點點呀<br />\n大家一齊去遊行呀 其實去完大家都知咩結果<br />\n最後邊個比人打姐 最後邊個因為負能量去跳樓<br />\n如果因為佢一席話 令到更多人受傷害<br />\n佢都唔會開心 唔表態都有佢既原因<br />\n<br />\n但當然如果當日佢有表態 而答案係支持既<br />\n我相信好多人都會封佢真英雄<br />\n我自己都好想佢表態站係我地雞蛋呢一邊<br />\n大是大非有個自己一直跟隨好耐既兄弟去支持係好唔同<br />\n我都慶幸我從來唔係咩麟伯 鍾咩咩既歌/影迷<br />\n如果你知道你追隨既人站係邪惡既一方<br />\n你個心仲唔會好過<br />\n<br />\n好慶幸我細個聽森美移動大<br />\n佢地個個都有良心既人<br />\n自己追隨既人站係自己既身旁係會有好大既鼓舞<br />\n唔表態都係一種表態<br />\n總好過撐警大會你見到佢係何妖旁邊<br />\n你再見到個撐警大會劉馬車同佢一齊影相<br />\n果刻你唔會好受得過依家<br />\n<br />\n純粹個人意見/睇法<br />\n<br />\n預左比人話達狗打手加上我自己係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水洗唔清<br />\n<br />\n加多句：年輕人 真係唔好再輕生<br />\n留得清山在！你死左唔係對件事有幫助<br />\n我同你互不相識 我都會為你流下眼淚<br />\n更何況你地屋企人 就算係紅底都好<br />\n你有命就可以感化佢地 你死左係乜都做唔到<br />\n勾踐臥薪嘗膽 有命就仲有希望<br />\n你要輕生不如做更有意義既野<br />\n諗下點上位 再幫下一班無助既人 去改變個社會"},{"pid":"55a8312410f4561f8bc50f4d54c46497ea9d1215","tid":1288654,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5d58afc5fe74462538aac48693a0f73cb97347","tid":1288654,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"我認為佢係俾人故意狙擊<br />\n點解咁多KOL唔恰，就係恰佢？<br />\n因為佢平時啲冤屈好多都自己吞咗佢唔出聲算<br />\n轉game世界大戰如是<br />\nbackup佢事件如是<br />\n今次唔出聲，終於搞到收唔到科<br />\n<br />\n本人真誠相信，佢嘅立場不變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"Backup佬事件係冤屈? 你到底有無留意事情發展"},{"pid":"a899fc7119c066541555871a9981ca8c210c4055","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a8312410f4561f8bc50f4d54c46497ea9d1215","tid":1288654,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5d58afc5fe74462538aac48693a0f73cb97347","tid":1288654,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"我認為佢係俾人故意狙擊<br />\n點解咁多KOL唔恰，就係恰佢？<br />\n因為佢平時啲冤屈好多都自己吞咗佢唔出聲算<br />\n轉game世界大戰如是<br />\nbackup佢事件如是<br />\n今次唔出聲，終於搞到收唔到科<br />\n<br />\n本人真誠相信，佢嘅立場不變"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"Backup佬事件係冤屈? 你到底有無留意事情發展"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:08:55.000Z","msg":"達哥 你終於黎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8563c7566dd3c308a845cd9791e8d240ad9ddb","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42ff8265c2a4001363acb51c7ba86eaa8f1d585","tid":1288654,"uid":71657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"每見到一個為達哥平反嘅post<br />\n就對達哥多一分反感 唔知點解"},{"pid":"67a44eaac4c4aa570ff5450e1b4ca63e7bb9c98f","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"563a3ebec99e3a350f502b37d0d990f5b60b987e","tid":1288654,"uid":262647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:07:22.000Z","msg":"預左比人屌<br />\n唔係為達哥平反 只係純粹個人表達<br />\n我覺得公眾人物都有佢既因素<br />\n佢公開帶頭係呀 呢個政權係點點點點呀<br />\n大家一齊去遊行呀 其實去完大家都知咩結果<br />\n最後邊個比人打姐 最後邊個因為負能量去跳樓<br />\n如果因為佢一席話 令到更多人受傷害<br />\n佢都唔會開心 唔表態都有佢既原因<br />\n<br />\n但當然如果當日佢有表態 而答案係支持既<br />\n我相信好多人都會封佢真英雄<br />\n我自己都好想佢表態站係我地雞蛋呢一邊<br />\n大是大非有個自己一直跟隨好耐既兄弟去支持係好唔同<br />\n我都慶幸我從來唔係咩麟伯 鍾咩咩既歌/影迷<br />\n如果你知道你追隨既人站係邪惡既一方<br />\n你個心仲唔會好過<br />\n<br />\n好慶幸我細個聽森美移動大<br />\n佢地個個都有良心既人<br />\n自己追隨既人站係自己既身旁係會有好大既鼓舞<br />\n唔表態都係一種表態<br />\n總好過撐警大會你見到佢係何妖旁邊<br />\n你再見到個撐警大會劉馬車同佢一齊影相<br />\n果刻你唔會好受得過依家<br />\n<br />\n純粹個人意見/睇法<br />\n<br />\n預左比人話達狗打手加上我自己係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水洗唔清<br />\n<br />\n加多句：年輕人 真係唔好再輕生<br />\n留得清山在！你死左唔係對件事有幫助<br />\n我同你互不相識 我都會為你流下眼淚<br />\n更何況你地屋企人 就算係紅底都好<br />\n你有命就可以感化佢地 你死左係乜都做唔到<br />\n勾踐臥薪嘗膽 有命就仲有希望<br />\n你要輕生不如做更有意義既野<br />\n諗下點上位 再幫下一班無助既人 去改變個社會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> P牌唔係問題<br />\n追擊達哥果班，好多都好細No.，好多係波台元老，本身就同達哥有私怨<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想其他連登仔好好思考下，咩先係做實事<br />\n私怨，或者做其他KOL打手果批，本身就係對人不對事<br />\n唔好將同路人推去對面 先最重要"},{"pid":"3208e28e553d15df7aa64efee12379ab6064375d","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9293d3d5ec2e806af88d529440f6ec00ac67d7","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49b6363b7a7a696b6f6108be1bc0c6ab90cded4","tid":1288654,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba41a609d16bf6109a29514c8e69cd11fef0790","tid":1288654,"uid":121102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited